Summary: Taking Pictures of Sky Fuzzy object same as report 19048
divs: Sighting DetailsAfter reading many reports of people taking random pictures of the sky, I and my main squeeze decided to start doing the same. We have captured quite a number odd objects in the sky using this method. One pic appears to corroborate pictures taken in NY recently. (report 19048)My cheap camera takes a pic every three secondso submitted is 2 pics, one of the object and another 3 secs later without he object. I don't have any picture editing software, but the picture is readily viewable in Windows Picture Viewer. Object is top right and to the right of the jet contrail. Please compare my pic to the NY pics.
